Global Rotary Surface Grinders Market Insights
Rotary Surface Grinders Market size was valued at USD 1.15 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 1.82 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Rotary Surface Grinders Market Overview
The global rotary surface grinders market is expected to experience significant growth over the forecast period, driven by the increasing demand for high-precision grinding machines across various industries. The market value of rotary surface grinders is projected to reach USD 2.5 billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 5.4%. This growth is largely attributed to advancements in manufacturing technologies, the rising need for efficient metal processing, and the expansion of industries such as automotive, aerospace, and electronics. The growing trend of automation in manufacturing processes is also driving the adoption of rotary surface grinders.

